  "commit_message": "[XLA:GPU] Respect PrecisionConfig::HIGHEST in DotAlgorithmRewriter and xtile codegen.\n\nPrevent downgrading F32 dots to BF16 when HIGHEST precision is explicitly requested, even if xla_gpu_default_to_alg_dot_bf16_bf16_f32 flag is enabled.\n\nThis fixes precision issues in Cholesky, SVD, QR, Eig, and TriangularSolve tests when the flag is enabled by default.\n\nPiperOrigin-RevId: 926694842",
